  "title": "Brand Communications Lead (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Shape your future with mentors who invest in you.</strong></em></p><p>Here at <strong>DASH</strong>, we’re on a mission to lead the sales and marketing world. Backed by leading companies, we champion their brands with heart and conviction. If you’re driven, ambitious, and ready to grow, we’d love for you to join us on this journey!<br /></p><p><em><strong>🍎 About Your Role:</strong></em></p><ul><li>Communicating face-to-face with real people, cultivating meaningful interactions and converting leads into loyal customers</li><li>Mentoring and developing a team towards aligned goals </li><li>Honing sales skills through ethical and effective strategies<br /></li></ul><p><strong>🤨 What’s in it for you?</strong></p><ul><li>Tailored 1-on-1 Mentorship and Continuous Guidance</li><li>Collaborative and Energising Team Vibes</li><li>Performance-based: Leadership & Career Advancement</li><li>Travelling Opportunities for Personal & Professional Growth</li></ul><p><br /><strong>📌 Here’s what we need</strong>:</p><ul><li>The Kind of Person who makes Mondays feel like Fridays</li><li>Always Willing to Learn and Give their Best</li><li>People Who Value Teamwork and Shared Success</li></ul><p><br />If you’re curious, looking for a career-change to switch things up a little or figuring out where to start your journey into working adult, give yourself a chance and…<br /></p><p><em><strong>‼️‼️APPLY NOW❤️‍🔥❤️‍🔥‼️‼️</strong></em></p>",
